{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":235642,"originalJapaneseLine":"揃ってお腹を押さえた。","translatedEnglishLine":"They both held their stomachs."},{"lineNumber":235643,"originalJapaneseLine":"「終わったら、美味しいご飯食べようねー」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Let's eat a delicious meal once this is over.\""},{"lineNumber":235644,"originalJapaneseLine":"「＜エール＞さん！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"<Yell>!\""},{"lineNumber":235645,"originalJapaneseLine":"「わあ、ビックリ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Wow, that surprised me!\""},{"lineNumber":235646,"originalJapaneseLine":"「今日のブロビオ選手との戦い頑張って下さいね！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Good luck with today's match against player Brobio!"},{"lineNumber":235647,"originalJapaneseLine":"　それはもうギッタンギッタンに","translatedEnglishLine":"Make sure you thoroughly beat him up"},{"lineNumber":235648,"originalJapaneseLine":"　やっつけちゃって下さい！」","translatedEnglishLine":"and finish him off!\""},

{"lineNumber":235649,"originalJapaneseLine":"「な、なんか怒ってる！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"A-Are you angry or something!?\""},

{"lineNumber":235650,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そりゃ怒りますよ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Of course I'm angry!"},

{"lineNumber":235651,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あの人、これまでに何度私にセクハラしたか！」","translatedEnglishLine":"How many times has that guy harassed me?!\""},

{"lineNumber":235652,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ぷんぷん！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmph!"},

{"lineNumber":235653,"originalJapaneseLine":"　私、あの人、大っ嫌い！」","translatedEnglishLine":"I really hate that guy!\""},

{"lineNumber":235654,"originalJapaneseLine":"「＜エール＞さん！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"<Yell>!"},

{"lineNumber":235655,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あんな人、ばしーんと倒しちゃって下さい！","translatedEnglishLine":"Please just knock that kind of person down with a bang!"},

{"lineNumber":235656,"originalJapaneseLine":"　もう私が許しちゃいますよ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'll forgive you myself!\""},

{"lineNumber":235657,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そんな自分勝手な……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"That's so selfish...\""},

{"lineNumber":235658,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あ、あはは……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, haha...\""},

{"lineNumber":235659,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あ、＜エール＞。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, <Yell>."},

{"lineNumber":235660,"originalJapaneseLine":"　そろそろ薬を飲んでおいた方が","translatedEnglishLine":"Maybe it's about time you took your medicine,"},

{"lineNumber":235661,"originalJapaneseLine":"　いいんじゃないか？」","translatedEnglishLine":"don't you think?\""},

{"lineNumber":235662,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そうだねえ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yeah, that's right."},

{"lineNumber":235663,"originalJapaneseLine":"「アームズさんも言ってたけど、","translatedEnglishLine":"Arms-san also said this,"},

{"lineNumber":235664,"originalJapaneseLine":"　この薬の効果はちょっと特殊だから気をつけてね」","translatedEnglishLine":"so be careful because this medicine's effect is a bit unusual.\" "},

{"lineNumber":235665,"originalJapaneseLine":"「回復薬でも予防薬でもなくて、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It's neither a healing medicine nor a preventive medicine,"},

{"lineNumber":235666,"originalJapaneseLine":"　毒を受けてもしばらくすれば、","translatedEnglishLine":"but even if you're poisoned, after a while,"},

{"lineNumber":235667,"originalJapaneseLine":"　すぐに治る薬とかなんとか」","translatedEnglishLine":"it supposedly cures you right away or something like that.\" "},

{"lineNumber":235668,"originalJapaneseLine":"「逆に言えば、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Put the other way,"},

{"lineNumber":235669,"originalJapaneseLine":"　毒を受けたらその効果はしばらく","translatedEnglishLine":"if you get poisoned, the effects will appear for a while"},

{"lineNumber":235670,"originalJapaneseLine":"　現れてしまうってことだから注意だよ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"so you have to be careful, okay?\""},

{"lineNumber":235671,"originalJapaneseLine":"あなたは頷いてから、","translatedEnglishLine":"You nodded, then"},

{"lineNumber":235672,"originalJapaneseLine":"錠剤の薬をごくりと飲み込んだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"swallowed the pill medicine in one gulp."},

{"lineNumber":235673,"originalJapaneseLine":"「＜エール＞選手！　入場願います！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Player <Yell>, please enter the arena!\""},

{"lineNumber":235674,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うおっ、来た来た来た！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Whoa, here they come, here they come!\""},

{"lineNumber":235675,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お姉ちゃん達はここから応援してるからね！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Your sisters will be cheering for you from here!\""},

{"lineNumber":235676,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あんなムカつく奴、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"That irritating guy,"},

{"lineNumber":235677,"originalJapaneseLine":"　すぱーんと倒しちまえよな！　相棒！」","translatedEnglishLine":"just knock him flat, alright, partner!\""},

{"lineNumber":235678,"originalJapaneseLine":"あなたは二人に見送られて試合場へ向かった。","translatedEnglishLine":"You headed toward the arena accompanied by the two of them."},

{"lineNumber":235679,"originalJapaneseLine":"　","translatedEnglishLine":""},

{"lineNumber":235680,"originalJapaneseLine":"　　＜わあああああああああああああ！！！！＞","translatedEnglishLine":"      <Waaaaaaaaaaaaah!!!!>"},

{"lineNumber":235681,"originalJapaneseLine":"一回戦と同様に、","translatedEnglishLine":"Like in the first round,"},

{"lineNumber":235682,"originalJapaneseLine":"観客の歓声があなたを出迎えてくれた。","translatedEnglishLine":"the crowd's cheers welcomed you."},

{"lineNumber":235683,"originalJapaneseLine":"『龍の方角より現れました！","translatedEnglishLine":"'Appearing from the direction of the Dragon!"},

{"lineNumber":235684,"originalJapaneseLine":"　法王の血を引く天才！　＜エール＞選手！","translatedEnglishLine":"The genius descended from papal blood! Player <Yell>!"},

{"lineNumber":235685,"originalJapaneseLine":"　今回はどのような戦いを見せてくれるのか！』","translatedEnglishLine":"What kind of battle will they show us this time!'"},

{"lineNumber":235686,"originalJapaneseLine":"　","translatedEnglishLine":""},

{"lineNumber":235687,"originalJapaneseLine":"　　＜わああああああああああ！＞","translatedEnglishLine":"      <Waaaaah!>"},

{"lineNumber":235688,"originalJapaneseLine":"『さあ、そして……』","translatedEnglishLine":"'Now, and then...'"},

{"lineNumber":235689,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ケヒヒヒヒヒヒ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Kehihihihihi...\""},

{"lineNumber":235690,"originalJapaneseLine":"『鬼の方角より現れしは、","translatedEnglishLine":"'Appearing from the direction of the Oni,"},

{"lineNumber":235691,"originalJapaneseLine":"　女は犯す男は殺す！　極悪ヒール！","translatedEnglishLine":"A woman who violates, a man who kills! The evil heel!"},

{"lineNumber":235692,"originalJapaneseLine":"　魔物隊長ブロビオ選手です！』","translatedEnglishLine":"It's the monster captain, player Brobio!'"},

{"lineNumber":235693,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おーっと、前の試合ではしゃぎすぎたから、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh-ho, maybe I got disliked because I overdid it in the last match,"},

{"lineNumber":235694,"originalJapaneseLine":"　嫌われちまったかな？　ケッケッケッ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"didn't I? Kekekeke...\""},

{"lineNumber":235695,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………。」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"............\""},

{"lineNumber":235696,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そんな怖い顔しねぇでくれよ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Don't make such a scary face, please."},

{"lineNumber":235697,"originalJapaneseLine":"　そんな力んでると勝てる戦いも勝てなくなるぜ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"If you tense up like that, you won't win even the fights you could win, you know?\""},

{"lineNumber":235698,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そういやよ、お前のパートナー……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"By the way, your partner..."},

{"lineNumber":235699,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あれはいいねぇ……","translatedEnglishLine":"That's something else, huh..."},

{"lineNumber":235700,"originalJapaneseLine":"「世の中には悪意なんてないって信じてる奴の顔だ。","translatedEnglishLine":"She has the face of someone who believes there's no malice in the world."},

{"lineNumber":235701,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ああいう女をグチャグチャにするのは……","translatedEnglishLine":"To crush a woman like that into pieces is...\""}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 揃ってお腹を押さえた。
「終わったら、美味しいご飯食べようねー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Let's eat a delicious meal once this is over."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「＜エール＞さん！」
「わあ、ビックリ！」
「今日のブロビオ選手との戦い頑張って下さいね！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Good luck with today's match against player Brobio!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それはもうギッタンギッタンに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Make sure you thoroughly beat him up

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やっつけちゃって下さい！」
「な、なんか怒ってる！？」
「そりゃ怒りますよ！
あの人、これまでに何度私にセクハラしたか！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: How many times has that guy harassed me?!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぷんぷん！
私、あの人、大っ嫌い！」
「＜エール＞さん！
あんな人、ばしーんと倒しちゃって下さい！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Please just knock that kind of person down with a bang!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう私が許しちゃいますよ！」
「そんな自分勝手な……
「あ、あはは……」
「あ、＜エール＞。
そろそろ薬を飲んでおいた方が
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Maybe it's about time you took your medicine,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いいんじゃないか？」
「そうだねえ」
「アームズさんも言ってたけど、
この薬の効果はちょっと特殊だから気をつけてね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so be careful because this medicine's effect is a bit unusual."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「回復薬でも予防薬でもなくて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's neither a healing medicine nor a preventive medicine,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 毒を受けてもしばらくすれば、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but even if you're poisoned, after a while,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すぐに治る薬とかなんとか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: it supposedly cures you right away or something like that."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「逆に言えば、
毒を受けたらその効果はしばらく
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: if you get poisoned, the effects will appear for a while

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 現れてしまうってことだから注意だよ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so you have to be careful, okay?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは頷いてから、
錠剤の薬をごくりと飲み込んだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: swallowed the pill medicine in one gulp.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「＜エール＞選手！　入場願います！」
「うおっ、来た来た来た！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Whoa, here they come, here they come!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お姉ちゃん達はここから応援してるからね！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Your sisters will be cheering for you from here!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あんなムカつく奴、
すぱーんと倒しちまえよな！　相棒！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: just knock him flat, alright, partner!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは二人に見送られて試合場へ向かった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You headed toward the arena accompanied by the two of them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜わあああああああああああああ！！！！＞
一回戦と同様に、
観客の歓声があなたを出迎えてくれた。
『龍の方角より現れました！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Appearing from the direction of the Dragon!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 法王の血を引く天才！　＜エール＞選手！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The genius descended from papal blood! Player <Yell>!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今回はどのような戦いを見せてくれるのか！』
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What kind of battle will they show us this time!'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜わああああああああああ！＞
『さあ、そして……』
「ケヒヒヒヒヒヒ……」
『鬼の方角より現れしは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Appearing from the direction of the Oni,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女は犯す男は殺す！　極悪ヒール！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A woman who violates, a man who kills! The evil heel!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物隊長ブロビオ選手です！』
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's the monster captain, player Brobio!'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おーっと、前の試合ではしゃぎすぎたから、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh-ho, maybe I got disliked because I overdid it in the last match,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 嫌われちまったかな？　ケッケッケッ……」
「そんな怖い顔しねぇでくれよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Don't make such a scary face, please.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そんな力んでると勝てる戦いも勝てなくなるぜ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you tense up like that, you won't win even the fights you could win, you know?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そういやよ、お前のパートナー……
あれはいいねぇ……
「世の中には悪意なんてないって信じてる奴の顔だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She has the face of someone who believes there's no malice in the world.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ああいう女をグチャグチャにするのは……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: To crush a woman like that into pieces is..."
